00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
 This time appearing is compassion, compassion.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:14.000
 And that also means this satyana samadhi is not negation, negative state as we discussed yesterday.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:21.000
 And as you all know, basically, it's called great emptiness, great emptiness of yoga and so forth.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:26.000
 But it's not negation state, emptiness that you already mind we think.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
 Think, think, that is not emptiness at all.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
 This emptiness is beyond duality, that's all about.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:43.000
 And that great emptiness is not negation, negative, not the blank state.

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:49.000
 This is full of opportunity, full of energy, vitality of that.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:56.000
 And this time that vitality is then compassion.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:01.000
 But that vitality, that is compassion.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:07.000
 And again, this compassion arises magically,

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:14.000
 magically as almost like breathing the wind in the space.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:23.000
 This can be so soothing, calming, without any partiality, without any restrictions.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:31.000
 That energy of compassion is spread out instantly to whole beings of six realms.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:39.000
 Everyone touched, or that compassion touched everyone, every single living being.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:44.000
 But just focus on the compassion, not individual beings.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:50.000
 That power, energy is just spread out without any restrictions.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:56.000
 That is known as all arising samadhi.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:03.000
 That all arising samadhi and that satyana samadhi is never separated.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:12.000
 Both are in one single status, status, status, just identical.

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.000
 There is no even separations.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:20.000
 But yet, actively we now let a concentrate on that energy.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:26.000
 This is known as then compassion that has no focus.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:30.000
 That compassion that has no partiality.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:34.000
 In the debate, in the teaching said mukwa mappaningi.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:38.000
 Mukwa mappaningi means there is no really particular purpose.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:46.000
 You just spread out that vastness, compassion, that throw out in space.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:55.000
 All the space, all the universe, everything is completely filled with that great compassion.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:59.000
 Compassion, you relax in that state.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:03.000
 Just relax mind in that compassion status.

