 This is known as then is magical.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:11.000
 Sometimes in the teaching said magical samadhis.

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:19.000
 This magical samadhis, juma-tawatini, it is truly magical.

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:22.000
 It is just spread out to everyone.

